title: The Latest: Cubs start Ross at catcher; ALCS goes back to KC
text: > Sports The Latest: Cubs start Ross at catcher; ALCS goes back to KC Toronto Blue Jays' Kevin Pillar, right, is tagged out by Kansas City Royals third baseman Mike Moustakas as he slides into third base on an attempted triple during the eighth inning in Game 5 of baseball's American League Championship Series on Wednesday, Oct. 21, 2015, in Toronto. Third base umpire Laz Diaz looks on. (Frank Gunn/The Canadian Press via AP) MANDATORY CREDIT
